<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT77">
<l>taṟpeṉṉait tāṉaṟiyā ṉēlun taṭaṅkaṭalaik</l>
<l>kaṟkoṇṭu tūrtta kaṭalvaṇṇa ṉeṟkoṇṭa</l>
<l>vevviṉaiyum nīṅka vilaṅkā maṉamvaittā</l>
<l>ṉevviṉaiyu māyumāṟ kaṇṭu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if He—the ocean-natured [Lord] who filled up the vast sea with rocks—</l>
<l>Does not know my real nature,</l>
<l>He saw and set [His] unchanging heart [on me]</l>
<l>So that the cruel karman that had seized me leaves.</l>
<l>Oh, any karman shall perish [by His] seeing!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
